jnxCollectorMIB.name: jnxCollectorMIB
jnxCollectorMIB.contactinfo: Juniper Technical Assistance Center Juniper Networks, Inc. 1194 N. Mathilda Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: support@juniper.net
jnxCollectorMIB.description: Provides data about each of the Collector PICs on a router.

JnxCollPicStateDef.name: JnxCollPicStateDef
JnxCollPicStateDef.description: Identifies specific error conditions that may exist on a Collector PIC.

jnxCollGlobalCreatedFiles.name: jnxCollGlobalCreatedFiles
jnxCollGlobalCreatedFiles.description: The total number of file created by all the collector pics on the router since the last time the router was reset.

jnxCollGlobalOpenFiles.name: jnxCollGlobalOpenFiles
jnxCollGlobalOpenFiles.description: The total number of open collector files currently present on the router.

jnxCollPicIfTable.name: jnxCollPicIfTable
jnxCollPicIfTable.description: Data about each collector pic currently present on the router.

jnxCollPicIfEntry.name: jnxCollPicIfEntry
jnxCollPicIfEntry.description: Each entry provides information about a single Collector PIC. Each Collector PIC contains a single interface and is identified by its ifIndex.

jnxCollPicIfCreatedFiles.name: jnxCollPicIfCreatedFiles
jnxCollPicIfCreatedFiles.description: The total number of files created by this Collector PIC since the last time the PIC was reset.

jnxCollPicIfCreatedFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfCreatedFileRate
jnxCollPicIfCreatedFileRate.description: The number of files created per second, measured over the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollPicIfPeakCreatedFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfPeakCreatedFileRate
jnxCollPicIfPeakCreatedFileRate.description: The peak number of files created per second.

jnxCollPicIfExportedFiles.name: jnxCollPicIfExportedFiles
jnxCollPicIfExportedFiles.description: The total number of files exported by this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfExportedFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfExportedFileRate
jnxCollPicIfExportedFileRate.description: The number of files exported per second, measured over the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollPicIfPeakExportedFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfPeakExportedFileRate
jnxCollPicIfPeakExportedFileRate.description: The peak number of files exported per second.

jnxCollPicIfDestroyedFiles.name: jnxCollPicIfDestroyedFiles
jnxCollPicIfDestroyedFiles.description: The total number of files destroyed by this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfDestroyedFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfDestroyedFileRate
jnxCollPicIfDestroyedFileRate.description: The number of files destroyed per second, as measured over the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollPicIfPeakDestroyedFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfPeakDestroyedFileRate
jnxCollPicIfPeakDestroyedFileRate.description: The peak number of files destroyed per second.

jnxCollPicIfProcRecords.name: jnxCollPicIfProcRecords
jnxCollPicIfProcRecords.description: The total number of flow records processed by this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfProcRecordsRate.name: jnxCollPicIfProcRecordsRate
jnxCollPicIfProcRecordsRate.description: The number of flow records processed per seconds, measured during the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollPicIfPeakProcRecordsRate.name: jnxCollPicIfPeakProcRecordsRate
jnxCollPicIfPeakProcRecordsRate.description: The peak number of flow records processed.

jnxCollPicIfMemoryUsed.name: jnxCollPicIfMemoryUsed
jnxCollPicIfMemoryUsed.description: The amount of memory used, in bytes, by this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfMemoryFree.name: jnxCollPicIfMemoryFree
jnxCollPicIfMemoryFree.description: The amount of memory free, in bytes, on this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfFtpBytes.name: jnxCollPicIfFtpBytes
jnxCollPicIfFtpBytes.description: The total number of bytes transferred via FTP by this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfFtpByteRate.name: jnxCollPicIfFtpByteRate
jnxCollPicIfFtpByteRate.description: The number of bytes per second transfered via FTP measured during the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollPicIfPeakFtpByteRate.name: jnxCollPicIfPeakFtpByteRate
jnxCollPicIfPeakFtpByteRate.description: The peak number of bytes per second transferred via FTP.

jnxCollPicIfFtpFiles.name: jnxCollPicIfFtpFiles
jnxCollPicIfFtpFiles.description: The total number of files transferred via FTP by this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfFtpFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfFtpFileRate
jnxCollPicIfFtpFileRate.description: The number of files per second transferred via FTP.

jnxCollPicIfPeakFtpFileRate.name: jnxCollPicIfPeakFtpFileRate
jnxCollPicIfPeakFtpFileRate.description: The peak number of files per second transferred via FTP.

jnxCollPicIfFtpFailures.name: jnxCollPicIfFtpFailures
jnxCollPicIfFtpFailures.description: The total number of FTP transfer failures on this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfCurrentState.name: jnxCollPicIfCurrentState
jnxCollPicIfCurrentState.description: The current state of various error conditions on this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfLastStateChange.name: jnxCollPicIfLastStateChange
jnxCollPicIfLastStateChange.description: Identifies the error condition that last changed state.

jnxCollPicIfStateChangeTime.name: jnxCollPicIfStateChangeTime
jnxCollPicIfStateChangeTime.description: The value of sysUpTime when the management subsystem last learned of a change to the value of jnxCollPicIfCurrentState for this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfStateChangeDate.name: jnxCollPicIfStateChangeDate
jnxCollPicIfStateChangeDate.description: The system date and time when the management subsystem last learned of a change to the value of jnxCollPicIfCurrentState for this Collector PIC.

jnxCollPicIfStateChangeType.name: jnxCollPicIfStateChangeType
jnxCollPicIfStateChangeType.description: This indicates whether the last state change set a new error condition or cleared an existing one.

jnxCollFileTable.name: jnxCollFileTable
jnxCollFileTable.description: Data about each collector file currently present on the router.

jnxCollFileEntry.name: jnxCollFileEntry
jnxCollFileEntry.description: Each entry provides information about a single file currently open on this Collector PIC. Each Collector PIC File is identified by the ifIndex associated with the Collector PIC and the name of the file.

jnxCollFileName.name: jnxCollFileName
jnxCollFileName.description: The name of a Collector File on this Collector PIC.

jnxCollFileFname.name: jnxCollFileFname
jnxCollFileFname.description: The name of a Collector File on this Collector PIC. This object is included for those NM applications that can't parse the file name from the instance portion of the OIDs and provides the value of jnxCollFileName explicitly.

jnxCollFileRecords.name: jnxCollFileRecords
jnxCollFileRecords.description: The number of flow records in this file.

jnxCollFileRecordRate.name: jnxCollFileRecordRate
jnxCollFileRecordRate.description: The number of flow records per second added to this file, measured during the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollFilePeakRecordRate.name: jnxCollFilePeakRecordRate
jnxCollFilePeakRecordRate.description: The peak number of flow records per second added to this file.

jnxCollFileUncompBytes.name: jnxCollFileUncompBytes
jnxCollFileUncompBytes.description: The number of uncompressed bytes in this file.

jnxCollFileUncompByteRate.name: jnxCollFileUncompByteRate
jnxCollFileUncompByteRate.description: The number of uncompressed bytes per second added to this file.

jnxCollFilePeakUncompByteRate.name: jnxCollFilePeakUncompByteRate
jnxCollFilePeakUncompByteRate.description: The peak number of uncompressed bytes per second added to this file.

jnxCollFileCompBytes.name: jnxCollFileCompBytes
jnxCollFileCompBytes.description: The number of compressed bytes in this file.

jnxCollFileCompByteRate.name: jnxCollFileCompByteRate
jnxCollFileCompByteRate.description: The number of compressed bytes per second added to this file, measured during the current 10 second interval.

jnxCollFilePeakCompByteRate.name: jnxCollFilePeakCompByteRate
jnxCollFilePeakCompByteRate.description: The peak number of compressed bytes per second added to this file.

jnxCollFileBlocks.name: jnxCollFileBlocks
jnxCollFileBlocks.description: The number of blocks in this file.

jnxCollFileCompBlocks.name: jnxCollFileCompBlocks
jnxCollFileCompBlocks.description: The number of compressed blocks in this file.

jnxCollFileTransferAttempts.name: jnxCollFileTransferAttempts
jnxCollFileTransferAttempts.description: The number of FTP transfer attempts for this file.

jnxCollFileState.name: jnxCollFileState
jnxCollFileState.description: The current state of this file.

jnxCollNotifyUrl.name: jnxCollNotifyUrl
jnxCollNotifyUrl.description: The URL associated with a file transfer destination.

jnxCollNotifyInetType.name: jnxCollNotifyInetType
jnxCollNotifyInetType.description: Used with jnxCollNotifyInetAddress to identify a specific file transfer destination.

jnxCollNotifyInetAddress.name: jnxCollNotifyInetAddress
jnxCollNotifyInetAddress.description: Used with jnxCollNotifyInetType to identify a specific file transfer destination.

jnxCollNotifyError.name: jnxCollNotifyError
jnxCollNotifyError.description: Description of error encountered when trying to transfer a file.

jnxCollNotifyFile.name: jnxCollNotifyFile
jnxCollNotifyFile.description: Identifies a specific file for notifications that refer to a file.

jnxCollNotifyFtpResultCode.name: jnxCollNotifyFtpResultCode
jnxCollNotifyFtpResultCode.description: Provides the FTP result code for file transfer notifications.

jnxCollNotifyFtpErrorText.name: jnxCollNotifyFtpErrorText
jnxCollNotifyFtpErrorText.description: Provides the FTP error text for file transfer notifications.

jnxCollNotifyMemUtil.name: jnxCollNotifyMemUtil
jnxCollNotifyMemUtil.description: Provides the current memory utilization for pic overload notifications.

jnxCollNotifyMemFree.name: jnxCollNotifyMemFree
jnxCollNotifyMemFree.description: Provides the current amount of free memory for pic overload notifications.

jnxCollNotifyMemThresh.name: jnxCollNotifyMemThresh
jnxCollNotifyMemThresh.description: Provides the current memory threshold used for determining memory unavailable conditions.

jnxCollNotifyNewRecordRate.name: jnxCollNotifyNewRecordRate
jnxCollNotifyNewRecordRate.description: Provides the current number of new records per second created on this Collector PIC.

jnxCollNotifyOverloadType.name: jnxCollNotifyOverloadType
jnxCollNotifyOverloadType.description: Identifies a specific type of flow overload condition on this Collector PIC.

jnxCollNotifyDate.name: jnxCollNotifyDate
jnxCollNotifyDate.description: Provides the current system date and time.

jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetType.name: jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetType
jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetType.description: Used with jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetAddress to identify a specific FTP server address.

jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetAddress.name: jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetAddress
jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerInetAddress.description: The FTP server address from which the switchover occurs.

jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerType.name: jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerType
jnxCollNotifyFromFtpServerType.description: The FTP server Type from which the switchover occurs.

jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetType.name: jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetType
jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetType.description: Used with jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetAddress to identify a specific FTP server address.

jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetAddress.name: jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetAddress
jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerInetAddress.description: The FTP server address to which the switchover occurs.

jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerType.name: jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerType
jnxCollNotifyToFtpServerType.description: The FTP server Type to which the switchover occurs.

jnxCollNotifyInitiatedBy.name: jnxCollNotifyInitiatedBy
jnxCollNotifyInitiatedBy.description: Identify what initiates the FTP switchover.

jnxCollNotificationPrefix.name: jnxCollNotificationPrefix
jnxCollNotificationPrefix.description: All collector notifications are registered under this branch.

jnxCollUnavailableDest.name: jnxCollUnavailableDest
jnxCollUnavailableDest.description: Notification of an unavailable destination failure encountered while transferring a collector file.

jnxCollUnavailableDestCleared.name: jnxCollUnavailableDestCleared
jnxCollUnavailableDestCleared.description: This indicates a previous unavailable destination failure has been resolved.

jnxCollUnsuccessfulTransfer.name: jnxCollUnsuccessfulTransfer
jnxCollUnsuccessfulTransfer.description: This indicates an error was encountered while attempting a file transfer.

jnxCollFlowOverload.name: jnxCollFlowOverload
jnxCollFlowOverload.description: This indicates a soft or hard flow overload condition has been triggered.

jnxCollFlowOverloadCleared.name: jnxCollFlowOverloadCleared
jnxCollFlowOverloadCleared.description: This indicates a soft or hard flow overload condition has been cleared.

jnxCollMemoryUnavailable.name: jnxCollMemoryUnavailable
jnxCollMemoryUnavailable.description: This indicates a memory unavailable condition has been triggered.

jnxCollMemoryAvailable.name: jnxCollMemoryAvailable
jnxCollMemoryAvailable.description: This indicates a memory unavailable condition has been cleared.

jnxCollFtpSwitchover.name: jnxCollFtpSwitchover
jnxCollFtpSwitchover.description: This indicates an FTP server switchover has occurred.
